{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"9":"Zakat (Kitab Al-Zakat)"},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1556,"hadithnumber_last":1700,"arabicnumber_first":1556,"arabicnumber_last":1700}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1652,"arabicnumber":1652,"text":"Rapporté par Anas رضي الله عنه : Le Messager d’Allah ﷺ a trouvé une datte et a dit : « Si je n’avais pas peur qu’elle fasse partie de la sadaqah, je l’aurais mangée. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (2055) Sahih Muslim (1071)"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":97}}]}